description: This is a short hike to do near Norris Point.  On the crest of the highway leading to the village, you will see signs for Jenniex House.  Park here and the trailhead is to the right.  The trail leads first to a viewing platform overlooking the Harbour and the hills/ Tablelands across it.The trail then descends the whole hill right to the Harbour via a well established trail.
directions: Main St Towards Norris Point.  the trailhead is at;  49°32'15.10"N,  57°53'0.19"W
title: James W. Humber Trail
